f our algorithm to correctly identify attacked\nsensors and securely reconstruct the state. Our simulations show that our\nmethod outperforms existing algorithms both in terms of optimality and\nexecution time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Mar 2019 22:24:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Jul 2019 08:34:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 4 Jul 2020 02:09:10 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 8 Oct 2020 03:39:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-09"}
