d a very efficient DFT algorithm in the\nmentioned basis, by estimating the corresponding matrix elements on a mesh, and\nby using a much finer mesh grid in the vicinity of nuclei.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Mar 2019 08:32:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-02"}
